odase.annotations

Annotation Type RangeFacets


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface RangeFacets
    Methods generated from OWL files for custom datatype properties will have this annotation, which gives the XSD facets for the custom datatype. Depending on the type, a field will be either -1, "" or {} to indicate that the particular facet is not present.
